John_McClane http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_McClane 0 Detective Lieutenant John McClane is a fictitious character and main protagonist of the Die Hard film series. Portrayed by Bruce Willis, he is known for his sardonic one-liners, including the famous catchphrase "Yippee-ki-yay, motherfucker".
